Package ide.backend.model.variables

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractRefVariabelModel
    This class represents the common base for references to variables (RefMemberModel and RefVariableModel) Common functions are defined in this class.
    AbstractVariableModel
    This class represents the common base for variables (MemberModel and VariableModel) Common functions are defined in this class.
    MemberModel
    This class represents the model for a block creating a new Member variable.
    PrintModel
    The model for the print function
    RefMemberModel
    This class represents a reference to a Member in the IDE.
    RefVariabelModel
    This class represents a reference to a variable in the IDE.
    SetModel
    Set model This model will set the variable [name] to the result of block [content]
    TypeModel
    This class represents a Type field in the IDE.
    ValueModel
    Represents an input value from the user This input could be a number, string etc
    VariableModel
    This class represents the model for a block creating a new variable.
